                                      reproduction could include bright flowers attracting butterflies that
                                      transfer pollen, flower nectar and odors that attract insects that
                                      transfer pollen, and hard shells on nuts that squirrels bury.]
                                          LS1.B.2 Construct a scientific explanation based on evidence for
